README.md
     1вҶ’# color
     3вҶ’Color lets you use colorized outputs in terms of [ANSI Escape
     4вҶ’Codes](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ANSI_escape_code#Colors) in Go (Golang). It
     5вҶ’has support for Windows too! The API can be used in several ways, pick one that
     6вҶ’suits you.
     7вҶ’
     8вҶ’![Color](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/438920/96832689-03b3e000-13f4-11eb-9803-46f4c4de3406.jpg)
     9вҶ’
    10вҶ’## Install
    12вҶ’```
    13вҶ’go get github.com/fatih/color
    14вҶ’```
