   142вҶ’### Disable/Enable color
   144вҶ’There might be a case where you want to explicitly disable/enable color output. the 
   145вҶ’`go-isatty` package will automatically disable color output for non-tty output streams 
      вҶ’вҖҰ
   177вҶ’## GitHub Actions
   179вҶ’To output color in GitHub Actions (or other CI systems that support ANSI colors), make sure to set `color.NoColor = false` so that it bypasses the check for non-tty output streams. 
